snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3702 - 23 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3702: Gada Pariwaar Ki Nayi Bahu
--------------------------------------------------------
Misa, a friend of Tapu's, shows up at the Gokuldham society to meet Tapu and give him his diary. Champaklal and Jetha enjoy seeing Tapu interacting warmly with his friend, and Bapuji thinks Misa could end up being their daughter-in-law. Jetha is taken aback by Champaklal's statements, while Sonu exhibits a depressed mood. Misha is brought over by Tapu, who also introduces her to his family. Bapuji is overjoyed to see her because he considers her to be cultured and well-educated. Tapu prevents Sonu from leaving the house while Misha compliments Tapu's coffee and denies having Sonu's tea. Bhide arrives at his balcony as well, where he is thrilled to see Misha with Tapu. Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3702, 23 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000210799

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 18 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 18 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 23rd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim

Fazila Qazi as Aneela

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3701 - Sonu Layi Tapu Ke Liye Nashta?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3702 - Gada Khandan Ki Hone Wali Bahu?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.description:
നമുക്ക് ഏറെ പ്രിയപ്പെട്ട സുബി സുരേഷ് കരൾരോഗം മൂലം മരണമടഞ്ഞ വാർത്ത എല്ലാവരെയും ഞെട്ടിച്ചു..

0:00 ആദരാഞ്ജലി
1:00 കരള്‍ നിലയ്ക്കുന്നത് എങ്ങനെ?
2:00 കരള്‍ രോഗത്തിന് കാരണം
3:34 അക്യൂട്ട് ലിവര്‍ ഫെയ്ലുവര്‍
7:00 സുബിക്ക് സംഭവിച്ചത് എന്തു ?
7:30 ഇതെങ്ങനെ തടയാം ? 
 41 വയസ്സിൽ കരൾരോഗം വന്നാൽ മരിക്കുമോ ? കരൾരോഗം വന്നാൽ ഒരാൾ മരണപ്പെടുന്നതെങ്ങനെ ? ഇതെങ്ങനെ തടയാം ? ഷെയർ ചെയ്യുക. ഒരുപാടുപേർക്ക് ഉപകാരപ്പെടുന്ന അറിവാണ്

snippet.title: Women Task Force | Purvi Disguises As A Maid And Fights With A Dangerous Killer | CID | 22 Feb 2023
snippet.description:
CID Officer fights with a dangerous killer which makes the case thrilling as the robber has a scary record of crimes. Daya, Purvi, and Pankaj planned a strategy to catch the criminals. How will team CID catch the criminals? To know more watch the full episode. 

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1310
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी #NewCID #LatestCID #CID2023

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more clips:
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIX5uRHs2F9qeuAy2R-6mCS9

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 19 Teaser - 23rd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 19 Teaser - 23rd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: $3 Trillion Lithium Found in J&K | Geopolitics of Natural Resources | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Recently, the ministry of mines announced that ∼ 60 lakh metric tonnes of lithium, or "white gold," or "new oil," had been found in Jammu and Kashmir. Although lithium has been discovered in India before, this is the first time such large quantities have been discovered. But what does this lithium mean for India's growth? Who will extract it? Is all of it actually mineable? When can we expect the results of the assessment? How can we exploit these reserves to their fullest potential? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee to find out!

Check Out the Mentioned Video - 

What if $1 = ₹1 happens? | Dollar vs Rupee Devaluation | Dhruv Rathee - https://youtu.be/tfLd329ovRI

snippet.title: 11K - Seedhe Maut
snippet.description:
Streaming Link: https://lnk.to/SeedheMaut11k

Music Credits
Written & Performed by Seedhe Maut
Produced by Calm
Mixed and Mastered by Vivek Thomas
Label: Azadi Records

Video Credits
Shot by: kyabc, Bhaktaaa, yashwithano
Editor: kyabc

2023 All Rights Reserved Azadi Records

Instagram: 
https://www.instagram.com/seedhemaut

Website:
https://www.seedhemaut.com/

Lyrics:

Calm: 

Haigi aisi Penmanship 
When I Let it rip 
Teri bae kahe damn 

Haige mere bohot known 
Game bana Warzone 
Aaja mere sheher verdansk 

Yaha padhe combo 
Down right django 
Haige thode crazy mans 

Jote cheene bouncer tera 
aaye jeb me meri 
mera street cred max 

Sm get paid in advance 
Milunga ya ni depends 
Bada bhai chalata benz 

Chota bhai chabata chain
Dono bhai jalate gaand 
Harr jagah 10 out of 10 

Hai bete bohot mehenga ye pen isse acche se aata hai karna offend 

Encore: 

Ise ache se aata hai karna  offend
Mujhse ache se bharna hai aata ghusend
Teri saath wali zada pasand 

Inki zaban se zada ye lunnd hai buland

Teri zaban se zada hai kaali surang
Tujhe jana hai to ja 
ive been one with the pen
Vaise 
Ghar wali music hai
Bahar waali business hai
Ek deri khushi
Aur ek deti 
Bhot sara eth aur bhot saare rupees
Aur moti mori jeb, T pe bade bade “louis”
I hold shit down on the map poora khudi
In halawo ki shakalein kyu aape aap sooji/suji?
Kavi kehena chahte hai ki ke jab kavi ne 
Aapke adarniya pitaji ke paiso ka kabhi khaya hi ni.., to..

To bollai tu kaise
Kala kiski kaisi
Bana khud ko pehele
Bana khud ke paise
Gawah khud ke jaise
Bada khud ke bhey se
Sambhal apne leheze
 bana  apni leh be
Aur chal apni leh pe 
Na chal kiska seh ke
Achal hu mai vaise 
Par apno pe aae to rehpte pe rehpte pe rehpte pe rehpte 
Mai seekha hu sadako se
Apno ke jhagado se
Kal se aur parso sey
Haatho se fisalke behete hue lamho se
Laundo ke khamakha bandi ke jhagado se
Fir unhi bandi ke 500 nakhro se

Mummy ki fikar se
Papa ke nasho se 
Seekha gareebi se 
Seekha tawajjo se
Seekha ke apno ko rakhne ka dil me aur
Dil se jo utare vo lawde pe bajo be ah

Calm: 

Hum jaisa kabhi ni banoge na 
Inn fudu se laundo ko bharu bhi na
Catalogue aisa ki maru bhi na
Dete jaara jote aur wo jalate gayi 
Me banata gaya
Reh gaya thoda maal jeb me flight thi Abj ne wo bhi Dabaaliya kahi 
Saala Dara bhi na 
Beta Zara bhi nahi 
Aur ye fuddu launde 
Aisa kare rap nahi 
Humse darta ye booth
Darega ni kaise hu bharta jab bhoot 
Hai ganda ye roop hai janta saboot
Ab inn rappero ko khaane me kantaal aaye dude par ye kaam hai 
launde dono bhare bhussi aisi meri Ma bhi puche kaha se aara hai paisa beta wo bhi pareshaan hai 

Encore : 

Tobhi ghoomu Sadako me galiyo me chain bahar chalu slow tez yaha pe  chale mera naam hai 
Sir

snippet.title: CID की Women Officers ने सिखाया एक Molester को सबक | CID | Best Of CID
snippet.description:
With DCP Chitrole now having joined forces with Marco, the whole team CID is left bewildered. As Marco and Chitrole plot to kill the CID inspectors who had gathered in a mall, Sachin and Kavin try to collect some information from witnesses. This eventually leads to Marco being arrested, but a bigger hand is discovered to be in play. Stay tuned to find out!

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode No: 1114
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #sonypal #cid2023 #latestcid #cidfullepisode 

Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonypali...

About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch the Best of CID episodes:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G3Tw9LL9pT_EQ1yNvFZYBhI

snippet.title: CLASS 10 FOOT PRINTS WITHOUT FEET FULL REVISION | ENGLISH ALL CHAPTERS | WATCH NOW WITH DEAR SIR
snippet.description:
Welcome to your YouTube channel Dear Sir! In this Live video, we present a comprehensive revision of all the Chapters from the Class 10 Foot Prints Without Feet English textbook. Whether you're a student preparing for your exams or simply looking to deepen your understanding of poetry, this video is perfect for you.

Join Dear Sir as he guides you through each chapter in the textbook, providing insightful commentary and analysis along the way. From "foot prints without feet" to "The Necklace," each Chapter is explored in depth, with a focus on understanding the themes, imagery, and literary devices used by the poets.

In addition to the full revision of each chapter, this video also includes sample questions and answers, designed to help you prepare for your exams and improve your critical thinking skills.

So, whether you're a student or simply a lover of Stories, don't miss this opportunity to gain a deeper understanding of the Class 10 foot prints without feet textbook. Watch now and join dear sir as we explore all the poems in this incredible collection.

Chapters names included in this book are:

1. A triumph of surgery
2. The Thief's story
3. The Midnight Visitor
4. Footprints Without Feet
5. The Making Of A Scienctist
6. The Necklace
7. Bholi
8. The Book That Saved The Earth

Also, Dont forget to share with your friends. 

Team Dear Sir

snippet.title: Shut Up Ya Kunal - Episode 24 - Kannan Gopinathan, Activist & former IAS
snippet.description:
Join us on this inspiring episode of Shut Up Ya Kunal as we sit down with Kannan Gopinathan, the former IAS officer and activist from Kerala who chose to resign from his post in protest against the restrictions imposed in Jammu and Kashmir. Through his powerful advocacy for democracy and fundamental rights, and his role as a leading figure in the Citizenship Amendment Act protests across India, we'll be motivated to ask questions, stand up for what we believe in, and fight for a better tomorrow.

Edited by - Ramit (youtube.com/c/OfficialPeeingHuman), Kartik Bansal
Producer - Nidhi Shetty
Audio-Video Team - Amin Jazayeri, Stuvi Krishnan, Kunal Waman
Location - Gray Spark Audio & Sound

Subscribe for more episodes of 'Shut Up Ya Kunal' and other upcoming videos.

snippet.title: Ep 3702 - SNEAK PEEK! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Holi Re Rasiya | Maithili Thakur x Seedhe Maut x Ravi Kishan x Mahan
snippet.description:
A modern take on an ever-loved brajbhashi delight, ‘Holi Re Rasiya’ is an ode to colour and joy. An eclectic mix of a classic interspersed with the fresh rap style from the lanes of the home land of Delhi - join us as we ring in and celebrate the festival of colours.

snippet.title: बिना दाल भिगोए दुनिया के सबसे नरम दही भल्ले बनाने का नया तरीका देखे इस वीडियो में आजSoft Dahi Bhalle
snippet.description:
बिना दाल भिगोए दुनिया के सबसे नरम दही भल्ले बनाने का नया तरीका देखे इस वीडियो में आजSoft Dahi Bhalle

#SoftDahiBhalle#NewRecipe#NirmlaNehraRecipes

Ingredients:-

For Vada:-
Semolina-1 cup
Green Chilli-1-2
Cumin Seeds-1 tsp
Ginger Paste-1 tsp
Salt-to taste
Oil-for frying

For Dahi Tadka:-
Curd-1/2 litre
Oil/Ghee-1-2 tsp
Chopped Ginger-1 tsp
Green Chilli-1-2
Mustard Seeds-1 tsp
Cumin Seeds-1 tsp
Asafoetida-a pinch
Chana Dal-1 tsp
Urad Dal-1 tsp
Curry Leaves-7-8
Red Chilli-1-2
Coriander Leaves

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3701 - 22 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3701: Tapu Ka Result
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha taunts Tapu for being a late riser, but Champaklal defends his grandson. Tapu surprises Jetha, and he gets shocked and falls over Bapuji. Jetha questions Tapu about his results, but somehow he tries to avoid the discussion. Jethalal's doubts get stronger, and he keeps on telling Tapu to show his final results. Tapu gets his result, and Jetha is startled to see that he flunked. Will Jetha be able to hold his temper this time after knowing Tapu's failure? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3701, 22 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3700 - 21 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3700: Tapu Ka Style
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu's gift distribution continues, and this time he reaches Sodhi's house. Sodhi gets a set of "Patiala Glass," and Gogi gets a t-shirt with a special message embossed on it. Similarly, Popatlal also gets new shades from Tapu, and he decides to wear them on his next meeting with his would-be wife. Sonu feels gratified that after Tapu's return, their Tapu Sena is finally united. Later, Sonu decides to make some delicious "Thepla" for Tapu, as he could really use some home-cooked food after such a long time. Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3700, 21 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000210415

snippet.title: Neha Rathore To NDTV: भांग के नशे में गीत नहीं लिखती हूं और मैं Criminal नहीं... | Khabron Ki Khabar
snippet.description:
लोक गायिका नेहा सिंह राठौर (Neha Singh Rathore) को यूपी पुलिस (UP Police) की तरफ से उनके गीत 'UP में का बा' को लेकर नोटिस जारी किया गया है. पुलिस द्वारा भेजे गए नोटिस को लेकर एनडीटीवी से बात करते हुए नेहा सिंह राठौर ने कहा कि वो इस नोटिस से डरी नहीं हैं.उन्होंने कहा कि मैं सिर्फ एक लोक गायिका हूं, इन बड़े नेताओं के सामने मैं कुछ भी नहीं हूं. 

About NDTV India (Hindi News Channel):

NDTV इंडिया भारत का सबसे विश्वसनीय हिन्दी न्यूज़ चैनल है, जो पॉलिटिक्स, बिज़नेस, खेल, बॉलीवुड और बहुत-से क्षेत्रों की ताज़ातरीन ख़बरें समूचे देश और दुनियाभर से आपके लिए लाता है. ख़बरों के अलावा NDTV इंडिया पर बड़ी राजनैतिक डिबेट्स, एक्सक्लूसिव इंटरव्यूज़, टॉक शोज़ भी चौबीसों घंटे लगातार चलते रहते हैं, जिनमें ढेरों भरोसेमंद जानकारी आप तक सभी प्लेटफॉर्मों - टीवी, इंटरनेट और मोबाइल - के ज़रिये पहुंचती है.

NDTV India is a 24-hour Hindi news channel. NDTV India established its image as one of India's leading credible news channels, and is a preferred channel by an audience which favours high quality local and world news, rather than sensational infotainment. NDTV India's popular shows revolve around: news, politics, economy, sports, entertainment, panel discussions with eminent personalities and noteworthy commentaries.

ताजातरीन Videos के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLpSN4vP31-Ku10h9c8jrTjSRFbFdQ8TR6

विधानसभा चुनाव 2023 की Full Coverage के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLpSN4vP31-KtYYtxdWWGL2G8umddUKcMl

NDTV इंडिया के सभी प्रीमियम शो एक साथ देखने के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/@ndtvindia/playlists?view=50&sort=dd&shelf_id=5

दिन की सबसे बड़ी ख़बरों पर NDTV के रिपोर्टरों और एंकरों की ग्राउंड रिपोर्ट तथा विश्लेषण के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLpSN4vP31-KvAM2r9mcbxfN7Jz9Dq3152

न्यूज़ इन शॉर्ट्स के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLpSN4vP31-Kv_xJpLn-dyJCVlTkqXB72R

देखें NDTV इंडिया लाइव, फ़्री डिश चैनल नं 49 पर

प्रमोटेड : सबसे शानदार शॉपिंग ऑफर्स पाने के लिए इस लिंक पर क्लिक करें - https://g360.in/3twKm3m

सबसे विश्वसनीय, निष्पक्ष और ताज़ातरीन ख़बरों के लिए हमारे चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करें.

snippet.description:
Jethalal, Bhide, Taarak and other society members enjoy the ‘Lodhi’ festival. Jetha caught Bhide when he was going to take food before celebrating the festival. Everyone enjoys the night a lot. Watch the full episode for hilarious moments. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 87
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.title: Carpool session 🚘 ft. @aashnahegde  @AshiKhanna  🎶
snippet.description:
Had a quick-chat/ karaoke and chill session with my favs. 
It was our first time in the all new e-SUV from Mahindra, the XUV400. Although I am not that fond of driving through the city traffic during the day, I was grateful to get my hands on this car that has single pedal drive technology and best in class cabin space. It also has 3 drive modes with throttle and steering response- fun, fast and fearless which made our stroll through the city peaceful and the 60+ connectivity features made it so enjoyable!

#XUV400 #MahindraXUV400 #AllElectric #paidpartnership https://mahindraelectricautomobile.com/xuv400

snippet.title: UP Vidhan Sabha: Akhilesh Yadav ने सांडों को लेकर Yogi Government पर कसा तंज। Akhilesh Yadav Speech
snippet.description:
Akhilesh Yadav Vidhan Sabha Speech: सांडों को लेकर अखिलेश ने Yogi Government पर कसा तंज | UP Budget

UP Vidhan Sabha Budget 2023: उत्तर प्रदेश विधानसभा में बजट पर चर्चा के दौरान अखिलेश यादव (Akhilesh Yadav) ने योगी सरकार (Yogi government) को जमकर घेरा. अखिलेश ने सदन में आवारा जानवरों का मुद्दा उठाया. सपा चीफ ने कहा कि आपके मंत्री कितने देश घूम आए कहीं सड़क पर सांड दिखाई दिया क्या. अखिलेश ने कहा कि जिन लोगों की जान जानवरों की वजह से गई है, मैं मांग करूंगा कि उनके परिवार को 10 लाख रुपये मुआवजा मिले.

hi.title: UP Vidhan Sabha: Akhilesh Yadav ने सांडों को लेकर Yogi Government पर कसा तंज। Akhilesh Yadav Speech
hi.description:
Akhilesh Yadav Vidhan Sabha Speech: सांडों को लेकर अखिलेश ने Yogi Government पर कसा तंज | UP Budget

UP Vidhan Sabha Budget 2023: उत्तर प्रदेश विधानसभा में बजट पर चर्चा के दौरान अखिलेश यादव (Akhilesh Yadav) ने योगी सरकार (Yogi government) को जमकर घेरा. अखिलेश ने सदन में आवारा जानवरों का मुद्दा उठाया. सपा चीफ ने कहा कि आपके मंत्री कितने देश घूम आए कहीं सड़क पर सांड दिखाई दिया क्या. अखिलेश ने कहा कि जिन लोगों की जान जानवरों की वजह से गई है, मैं मांग करूंगा कि उनके परिवार को 10 लाख रुपये मुआवजा मिले.

snippet.title: How George Soros can destroy India | Who is George Soros? | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video Abhi and Niyu discuss the controversial Billionaire George Soros and how he has used his genius and economic power to bring countries like Britain, Thailand, Malaysia, Japan to their knees!

#georgesoros #jaishankar #abhiandniyu 

George Soros is one of the most prominent and controversial figures in the world of finance, philanthropy, and politics. Born in Hungary in 1930, Soros emigrated to the United States in 1956 and quickly rose to prominence as a successful hedge fund manager and currency trader. In addition to his business pursuits, Soros has been a major player in the world of philanthropy, founding the Open Society Foundations, which support human rights, democracy, and free speech around the world.

Soros is also a vocal political activist, advocating for progressive causes and supporting political candidates and organizations that share his values. He has been a prominent critic of authoritarian regimes and has been particularly active in promoting democracy and human rights in Eastern Europe and other parts of the world.

Despite his many accomplishments and philanthropic efforts, Soros has also been the subject of controversy and criticism, particularly from those on the political right who view him as a threat to their agenda. Accusations have been made that he is part of a secret globalist conspiracy and that he uses his wealth and influence to manipulate world events to his advantage.

In this video, we will explore the life and career of George Soros, his philanthropic and political activities, as well as the controversies and conspiracy theories that have surrounded him. Join us as we delve into the complex world of one of the most influential and controversial figures of our time.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

snippet.title: Inspector Purvi ने Culprit को पकड़ा उसके ही तरीके से | CID | Full Episode | 18 Feb 2023
snippet.description:
CID is a crime show that will take you into the thrilling world of danger and criminals. The team will solve the cases and bring justice to people. They will leave no stone unturned in putting criminals behind the bars and saving innocent lives. We bring you the best of CID full episodes where you can join the ride and watch the team solve mysterious cases.

Show name: CID
Starcast: Shivaji Satam, Dayanand Shetty, Aditya Srivastav
Produced by: B.P. Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #sonypal 

Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonypali...

About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch the full episodes of CID:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list...

snippet.title: Thapki ने की Shraddha को बेनक़ाब करने की कोशिश | Thapki Pyar Ki | Full Episode | Ep. 631
snippet.description:
Thapki ने की Shraddha को बेनक़ाब करने की कोशिश | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 631

Thapki informs Amma Mai and her family that Shraddha has been impersonating her. Will they believe her? Later Bihaan comes up with a plan to expose Shraddha's sinister plot. Will he be successful?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?
